‪Ah, err...

00:01:56.783 --> 00:01:58.201
‪Saya, sungguh, sungguh minta maaf.

00:01:58.284 --> 00:02:00.203
‪Kami memang
‪seratus, seribu kali salah.

00:02:00.286 --> 00:02:01.454
‪Awak di mana sekarang?

00:02:01.538 --> 00:02:03.039
‪Saya nak jumpa awak dan
‪minta maaf sendiri.

00:02:03.123 --> 00:02:05.375
‪Sudahlah, dah selesai.

00:02:05.458 --> 00:02:08.128
‪Ah, Hyunjoo-ssi! Hyunjoo-ssi! Hyunjoo-ssi!
‪Tolong beri masa 5 minit saja, ya?

00:02:08.628 --> 00:02:11.047
