‪kenapa abang minta maaf macam tu,

00:02:48.376 --> 00:02:50.211
‪dan kenapa kita perlu minta maaf?

00:02:50.295 --> 00:02:52.630
‪Geon-woo, ini kerja
‪pertama kita, kan? Ya?

00:02:52.714 --> 00:02:55.341
